I"<p>This is WIP.</p>

<p>I am “thinking aloud” about the primitive elements of software.</p>

<p>I expect that the contents of this note will change with feedback and further thought.</p>

<p>I do, though, believe in “showing my work”.  Showing intermediate results, no matter how rough.</p>

<p>Although this article is fresh, these ideas have been percolating for several decades, influenced by my experiences in running a small software consultancy.</p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/guitarvydas/softwareatoms">Notes in Obsidian Format</a></p>

